        "content": "<p>One thing I tried was using another hypothesis: <br>\nh3: a^4 + b^4 = d^2 &and; a<em>b</em>d &ne; 0<br>\nbut in order to prove this hypothesis, I need to get rid of the \\exists d from h2. I tried using apply Exists.elim but it does not seem to work. Is there any way to work around this?<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/tnqidwZgY2FYvyDz8KE03xiG/Screenshot-2024-08-08-at-7.38.35PM.png\">Screenshot-2024-08-08-at-7.38.35PM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/tnqidwZgY2FYvyDz8KE03xiG/Screenshot-2024-08-08-at-7.38.35PM.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2024-08-08-at-7.38.35PM.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"1240x258\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/tnqidwZgY2FYvyDz8KE03xiG/Screenshot-2024-08-08-at-7.38.35PM.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
